title: Tyga arrives at Cairns hotel with a slew of Louis Vuitton luggage after partying in Sydney
text:
Tyga has been enjoying some time in Australia, and continued his tour Down Under on Saturday.

The 29-year-old arrvied at the Riley Hotel in Cairns, Queensland, ahead of his performance at the Grass is Greener festival.

The Rack City hitmaker certainly travels in style, with multiple Louis Vuitton items of luggage.

In town: Tyga (centre) arrived at Queensland hotel with burly bodyguards in tow on Saturday

The star pulled up to the hotel with two burly assistants, one of whom carried a multi-coloured Louis Vuitton duffel bag for him.

Tiger had a second Louis Vuitton piece in tow, another duffel bag, which he carried inside himself.

The rapper wore a black hoodie with the words Las Vegas emblazoned on the front across the right side of his chest.

Star power: The 29-year-old arrvied at the Riley Hotel in Cairns, Queensland, ahead of his performance at the Grass is Greener festival

Tough! The star pulled up to the hotel with two burly assistants, one of whom carried a multi-coloured Louis Vuitton duffel bag for him

Cute bag! Tiger had a second Louis Vuitton piece in tow, another duffel bag, which he carried inside himself

He paired the sweat tip with a white shirt which was worn underneath and could be visible peaking out beneath.

The fashionable look was elevated by a pair of eye-catching loose jeans with an unusual pattern featuring black and brown tie-dye smudges.

He finished the trendy ensemble with a pair of sneakers in an orange and black pattern.

On trend: The rapper wore a black hoodie with the words Las Vegas emblazoned on the front across the right side of his chest

Chic: The fashionable look was elevated by a pair of eye-catching loose jeans with an unusual pattern featuring black and brown tie-dye smudges

The star has had a ball during his time Down Under, enjoying the company of several young women in Sydney.

Some of those women have been identified as swimwear designer Katya Elise Henry, 25, and another young woman known simply as Sharon.

On Tuesday, Tyga embarked on a Sydney Harbour cruise aboard a luxury yacht, sharing photos of the outing to Instagram.
